{"tid":928512,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"nokia 9 pureview玉照  後置5鏡頭係咩玩法","createTime":"2018-12-05T01:28:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T21:38:20.000Z","uid":66943,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0fb17808c4aa8132d1db034e6deef62cf9dc48b4","tid":928512,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T01:28:55.000Z","msg":"nokia 9 PureView背部搭載五顆Penta-Lens蔡司認證鏡頭，五顆鏡頭呈六邊形排布，旁邊還有LED閃光燈和輔助對焦模塊，<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CJgHj35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCJgHj35.jpg&h=c3a1d9e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據此前的報導，nokia 9 PureView正面沒有劉海，採用5.9&quot;OLED，解像度為QHD，搭載Snapdragon 845，配備6/8GB RAM+128GB ROM，電池容量為4150mAh，行Android Pie系統，可能還支持IP68級防塵防水以及無線充電功能。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zkkMMJ5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzkkMMJ5.jpg&h=2d157c85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n　　由於沒有在目前的照片中看到指紋識別的位置，因此猜測nokia 9 PureView還可能採用屏下指紋技術。值得一提的是，HMD定於12月5日在杜拜舉辦活動，但屆時nokia 9 PureView亮相的可能性不高。"},{"pid":"fd1b9c4ba55a07f3eeec7fa7c1f6072fa9256d9b","tid":928512,"uid":61954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T01:34:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8d1a50f3809594d5c95fbad49d0f57a02dce02","tid":928512,"uid":66943,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fd1b9c4ba55a07f3eeec7fa7c1f6072fa9256d9b","tid":928512,"uid":61954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T01:34:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T01:37:13.000Z","msg":"左輪黎既喂"},{"pid":"3f6783ce06c56f54e04266d45837d4a21bc68387","tid":928512,"uid":62532,"